query:
INSERT INTO debian_repository_index_packages (
                            component_id,
                            architecture,
                            compression,
                            size,
                            contents,
                            md5sum,
                            sha1sum,
                            sha256sum,
                            created_at,
                            updated_at
                        )
                        VALUES (
                            $1,
                            $2::debian_repository_architecture,
                            NULL,
                            $3,
                            $4,
                            $5,
                            $6,
                            $7,
                            NOW(),
                            NOW()
                        )
